_______________________________________________________________________________
"Power Mastery"   
        This is a global power modifier allowing psionicists to become
        masters of X, where X is one of the other powers.  The power
        mastery ability itself must first be bought, then each
        individual power must be individually mastered.  There are 3
        levels of mastery.  The first causes all uses of the power to be
        automatically under the influence of enhance and costs 1
        purchase point.  The second causes all uses of the power to
        additionally be under the influence of dual mind and costs 1
        more purchase points.  The last reduces the sp cost of the power
        by a percentage of its normal cost and costs an additional
        purchase point.  Note that these benefits are in ADDITION to any
        enhance or dual mind which might might already be in effect!
        Power Mastery cannot be forgotten once learned, but the
        individual powers that are mastered can be 'unmastered'.
 
SP Cost:  none		Guild Level:  8	Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  none - use Guild Advance Board
